<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>多节点归集</title>
</head>
<body>
<%= require('@pages/common/public/header.ejs')() %>
<div class="container">
    <h1 style="text-align: center">多节点归集</h1>
    <h5 style="color: gray;text-align: center">所有代码运行均在本地</h5>

    <div class="input-group mb-3" style="margin-top: 10px">
        <div class="input-group-prepend">
            <span class="input-group-text" id="collection_text">归集地址</span>
        </div>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="collection" aria-describedby="basic-addon3">
    </div>

    <div class="row" style="margin-top: 40px">
        <div class="col-6">
            <label>输入地址「一行一个」</label>
            <textarea id="addresses" rows="10" style="width: 100%"></textarea>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary" id="submit" style="margin-top: 10px">提交</button>
        </div>

        <div class="col-6">
            <label>输入私钥「一行一个，每一行要和地址进行对应」</label>
            <textarea id="privates" rows="10" style="width: 100%"></textarea>

            <div class="input-group mb-3" style="margin-top: 10px">
                <div class="input-group-prepend">
                    <span class="input-group-text" id="threshold_text">阈值</span>
                </div>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="threshold" aria-describedby="basic-addon3" value="1000">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <ul>
        <li>本工具代码本地执行，请放心使用</li>
        <li>只会将被归集地址上超越阈值的地址全部转移到归集地址上</li>
        <li>左边地址，右边私钥，每一行要一一对应</li>
        <li>请不要留有空白行</li>
        <li>请在每个账户上放置一点 BNB 来充当燃料，小于 0.0005 的账号会忽略</li>
        <li>应该先<a href="/multicash.html">兑换支票</a>，再进行归集</li>
        <li>捐赠地址: 0xD1B260aba3bA6f3D3099725b1b1C7cdD12581974</li>
    </ul>

    <table class="table" style="margin-top: 10px">
        <thead>
        <tr>
            <th scope="col">#</th>
            <th scope="col">TX</th>
            <th scope="col">地址</th>
            <th scope="col">gas</th>
            <th scope="col">兑换</th>
            <th scope="col">状态</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody id="hex">
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
<div style="height: 30px;margin-top: 70px">

</div>
</body>
</html>
